THere are several different command servers, each running on a different TCP socket:

server   |  port name         | value | config file
questctl | QUEST_COMMAND_PORT | 3911  | questlib/quest.cfg


quest.cfg:QUEST_COMMAND_PORT 3911
quest.conf:TCS_COM_PORT                    1 	# which port of the TCS to use for serial communication
questsrv-daytime.cfg:QUEST_COMMAND_PORT 3913
tcs_talk.cfg:TCS_TALK_COMMAND_PORT 3913
weather_srv.cfg:WEATHER_COMMAND_PORT 3914

